title: Wanted Adventure
description:
Hey everyone! I’m Dana, an American living abroad in Germany. I make videos about the cultural differences between Germany and the USA, my own personal experiences as an American living abroad in Germany, and things that fascinate...or even sometimes frustrate me about languages and the German language in particular.

For more info, pics, and updates, check out the social media links below.

Thanks for watching!

title: Hayley Alexis
description:
Hey you guys, my name is Hayley if you did not know now you do. 

I am an American currently living in Germany and sharing my opinions. My idea of coming to Germany was supposed to be a temporary stay but has turned into a long journey of learning and sharing my experiences with the German culture. 

I talk about language, food and everything in-between. I hope if you landed here you made the decision to stay and I am so thankful that you have decided to stop by my channel! 


Love always, 
Hayley
